name: Sockfacts
0: ”Alexa, ask Sock Facts to tell me a fact.”
skdetail:

Invocation Name: sock facts
des:
This Alexa skill gives you all the information you need to know about socks. 
Once you've cycled all the facts in this app a few times you're going to be a small expert about those things we put between our feet and our shoes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
